title: 12th Region girls' soccer championship: PrepSpin live stream
text:
HERALD-LEADER Buy Photo 
Boyle County and West Jessamine, ranked No. 5 and No. 6 respectively in the latest Maher Rankings , meet in the girls' 12th Region soccer championship Thursday at West Jessamine. The game begins at 8 p.m. If you can't make it out to watch live, PrepSpin has a live stream broadcast. I've embedded the video below: 
The 12th Region winner will host the 11th Region winner (either No. 3 Lexington Catholic or Madison Central) on Tuesday at 7 p.m.
